---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="YouTube Thumbnail Masterclass - Approachable Design" description="Create great YouTube thumbnails without a designer. A self-paced workshop teaching timeless design principles for click-worthy thumbnails.">
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Hero -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-16">
        <span class="text-brand-purple text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">Video Workshop</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold mt-4 mb-6">
          Thumbnail Design Workshop
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/70 mb-8">
          Create great YouTube thumbnails (without a designer)
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          A self-paced workshop teaching how to create better YouTube thumbnails using timeless design principles rather than trends.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Problem -->
      <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-white/10 mb-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-6">
            You spent all that effort on your video but no one clicked. Why?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-lg">
            Your thumbnail is the first impression. Learn Netflix movie thumbnail strategies applied to YouTube, along with layout, typography, and contrast principles that actually work.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- What You'll Learn -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8 text-center">What You'll Learn</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Netflix Strategies</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60">Apply movie thumbnail strategies to your YouTube content.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Layout & Typography</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60">Master the fundamentals of visual hierarchy and text placement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Contrast Principles</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60">Make your thumbnails pop in a sea of competing content.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Figma Templates</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60">Create reusable templates for consistency across your channel.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Midjourney Integration</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60">Use AI to generate professional backgrounds.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2">Real-World Breakdowns</h3>
            <p class="text-white/60">Analysis of thumbnails from Colin & Samir, MrBeast, and more.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonials -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-8 text-center">What Students Say</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-white/80 italic mb-4">"I feel like I took away so many actionable heuristics and insights quickly."</p>
            <div>
              <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white">Jonny Miller</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Founder, Nervous System Mastery</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-white/80 italic mb-4">"The concrete tips about contrast and rule of thirds were especially helpful."</p>
            <div>
              <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white">Luca Dellana</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Author</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-white/80 italic mb-4">"We were buzzing with ideas for improving our branding. Templates made it approachable."</p>
            <div>
              <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white">Nat Eliason</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Writer & Entrepreneur</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-dark-light rounded-2xl p-6 border border-white/10">
            <p class="text-white/80 italic mb-4">"His design philosophy plus practical approach makes design accessible."</p>
            <div>
              <p class="font-heading font-semibold text-white">Michael Gendler</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/50">Co-founder, Ultraspeaking</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bonuses -->
